Description: RangeOS AI Tactical Desktop Shell
 Installs the RangeOS AI Electron-based tactical HUD shell.
 Provides the full multi-workspace interface including Red, Blue,
 Forensics, AI Assistant, Reports Center and Lab Builder workspaces.
